Our C-coded runtime.  Handles garbage collection,
calls to various OS services, linking of .o7 files
and hooks for periodic services like thread switching.

See:
     ./gc/README
     ROOT/doc/references

     Asynchronous Signals in Standard ML
     John H Reppy (Cornell)
     1990, 18p
     http://www.smlnj.org//compiler-notes/90-tr-reppy.ps



